        <div class="nbd-bold-sub-title">
			<h4>Our values are the principles that guide us. Along with our 7 culture principles, ‘The Nedbank Way’, it supports us achieving our strategic ambitions. The Nedbank Way describes our required culture and what we need to shift towards.</h4>
            <p>
				
					
				
				
			
