<div role="tabpanel" tabindex="0" class="cmp-tabs__tabpanel nbd-tabs-tabpanel " data-tabcontainer="item_1696403554814" data-cmp-hook-tabs="tabpanel"><div class="container responsivegrid">

    
    
    
    <div class="cmp-container">
        
        <div class="spacing">
    


<div class="clearfix responsive-spacing whitebg" style="--spacing-value: 64px;"></div></div>
<div class="quotation">
    



    <div class="container-fluid nbd-quotation">
    <div class="ng-container">
		
		
        <div class="nbd-bold-sub-title">
			<h4>Our strategy, represented by strategic value drivers and strategic value unlocks, provides a clear framework of where we need to focus as a purpose-led organisation and what we need to do to meet our medium- and long-term targets to create value for our shareholders and other stakeholders.</h4>
            <p>
				
					
				
				
			
			</p>
        </div>
	
    </div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="spacing">
    


<div class="clearfix responsive-spacing whitebg" style="--spacing-value: 48px;"></div></div>
<div class="container responsivegrid">

    
    
    
    <div class="cmp-container">
        
        
        
    </div>

</div>
<div class="rte">

<div class=" ng-container cmp-text nbd-rte-enc">
    <h2>Our strategic value drivers</h2>
<p> </p>
<p><b><span class="nbd-paragraph">Through our strategy we seek to grow revenue faster than expenses and increase levels of productivity, while maintaining world-class risk and capital management metrics to meet our medium- and long-term targets.</span></b></p>
<p> </p>
<h4>Growth</h4>
<p><span class="nbd-paragraph">To grow faster, we will focus on gaining profitable market share in key lending categories, increase our share of main-banked clients and related transactional deposits, and deliver market-leading client experiences to attract new clients and deepen our share of wallet among existing clients. We also look to unlock new growth opportunities, including the cross-sell of insurance products and portfolio diversification into East Africa and other new market segments, and leverage our modern technology platform for commercial value.</span></p>
<p> </p>
<h4>Productivity</h4>
<p><span class="nbd-paragraph">To boost productivity we are building on existing efforts to optimise our structure and operating model, as well as leveraging technologies such as AI and intelligent hyperautomation.</span></p>
<p> </p>
<h4>Risk and capital management</h4>
<p><span class="nbd-p3">Our world-class risk management capabilities ensure we balance risk and reward appropriately. Our CLR will be managed within our through-the-cycle target range of 60 bps to 100 bps, while capital levels will remain strong, supporting future growth.</span></p>

</div>

    







</div>
<div class="spacing">
    


<div class="clearfix responsive-spacing whitebg" style="--spacing-value: 80px;"></div></div>
<div class="contentblockv2">
    


    
    




    

    <div id="contentblockv2_278463">
    
        
        
        
            <section><div class="contentblock-container centredcontentblock">
    <div class="ng-container imageshadow  secondary-bg inline">
        <section class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12">
            <picture>
                <source media="(min-width: 1025px)" srcset="/content/dam/group/images/investor-relations/135-rivonia-night-motion-lights.jpg"/>
                <source media="(min-width: 768px)" srcset="/content/dam/group/images/investor-relations/135-rivonia-night-motion-lights.jpg/_jcr_content/renditions/cq5dam.resized.mobi548.png"/>
                <source media="(max-width: 767px)" srcset="/content/dam/group/images/investor-relations/135-rivonia-night-motion-lights.jpg/_jcr_content/renditions/cq5dam.resized.mobi320.png"/>
                <img srcset="/content/dam/group/images/investor-relations/135-rivonia-night-motion-lights.jpg"/>
            </picture>
            
        </section>
        <section class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12 contentsection">
            
<h3>We have set ambitious medium-term targets</h3>

<p><h5><b>In the short term, we aim for an increase in DHEPS in the low single digits and to achieve an ROE of 15% by the end of 2025. The group's CIR is expected to increase year-on-year.</b></h5>
</p>



        </section>
    </div>
</div></section>
        
        
        
        
    

    
    </div>

   </div>
<div class="spacing">
    


<div class="clearfix responsive-spacing whitebg" style="--spacing-value: 48px;"></div></div>
<div class="quotation">
    



    <div class="container-fluid nbd-quotation">
    <div class="ng-container">
		
		
        <div class="nbd-bold-sub-title">
			<h4>In the medium term, our ambition remains to progress our ROE to 17%, with our CIR below 54%. In the long term we remain committed to an ROE of 18% or more (around COE plus 3%) and to improve our CIR to below 50%.</h4>
            <p>
				
					
				
				
			
			</p>
        </div>
	
    </div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="spacing">
    


<div class="clearfix responsive-spacing whitebg" style="--spacing-value: 48px;"></div></div>
<div class="rte">

<div class=" ng-container cmp-text nbd-rte-enc">
    <h2>Strategic value unlocks</h2>
<p> </p>
<p><span class="nbd-p3">The Nedbank strategy outlines our actions to grow earnings, achieve a higher return on equity (ROE) and lower the cost-to-income ratio (CIR) over time. Our strategy is delivered through 5 strategic value unlocks: digital leadership (DX); market-leading client experiences (CX); areas that create value (strategic portfolio tilt); strategic growth vectors; and creating positive impacts. A skilled workforce supported by our modern technology platform is driving steady execution of our strategy to drive robust revenue growth and productivity enhancements, while we maintain strong risk and capital management metrics. In 2025 we concluded an organisational restructure; disposed of our financial investment in Ecobank Transnational Incorporated; acquired business payments fintech iKhokha; and made an offer to acquire c66% of NCBA shares.</span></p>

</div>

    







</div>
<div class="spacing">
    


<div class="clearfix responsive-spacing whitebg" style="--spacing-value: 48px;"></div></div>
<div class="illustrationcard">
    

    
    
    




    <div class="illustrationcardwrapper bg-grassgreen">
        <div class="ng-container">
            
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col">
                        <h3 aria-label="Our 5 strategic value unlocks">
                            Our 5 strategic value unlocks
                        </h3>
                    </div>
                </div>
            
            <div class="row nb-row ">

                
                    
                        
                            <!-- col-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4 -->
                            <div class="columnsitem 1"> 
                                <div class="card nb-card">
                                    <div class="card-header leftalignedillustration bordered-header border-bottom-0">
                                        <div class="icon-wrapper ">
                                            <img src="/content/dam/group/icons/strategic-value-unlock-icon-05.svg" alt="Digital leadership (DX) " class="card-icon"/>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="card-body border-top-0">   
                                        <h4>Digital leadership (DX) </h4>
                                        <p></p>
                                        
                                            <div class="description"><p>We seek to amplify the digital experience (DX) for our clients and employees by leveraging and commercialising our IT foundations and the investments made over the past few years. An enhanced digital experience increases client satisfaction, digital adoption, and improved client retention.</p>
</div>
                                        
                                        
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        
                            <!-- col-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4 -->
                            <div class="columnsitem 2"> 
                                <div class="card nb-card">
                                    <div class="card-header leftalignedillustration bordered-header border-bottom-0">
                                        <div class="icon-wrapper ">
                                            <img src="/content/dam/group/icons/strategic-value-unlock-icon-01.svg" alt="Market-leading client experiences (CX) " class="card-icon"/>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="card-body border-top-0">   
                                        <h4>Market-leading client experiences (CX) </h4>
                                        <p></p>
                                        
                                            <div class="description"><p>The ability to deliver exceptional client experiences (CX) is a crucial differentiator, supported by a strong competitive brand. Our aspiration is to be Africa’s #1 digital financial services provider by retaining a #1 position among South African banks, thereby enhancing our social capital.</p>
</div>
                                        
                                        
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        
                            <!-- col-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4 -->
                            <div class="columnsitem 3"> 
                                <div class="card nb-card">
                                    <div class="card-header leftalignedillustration bordered-header border-bottom-0">
                                        <div class="icon-wrapper ">
                                            <img src="/content/dam/group/icons/strategic-value-unlock-icon-02.svg" alt="Focusing on areas that create value (SPT) " class="card-icon"/>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="card-body border-top-0">   
                                        <h4>Focusing on areas that create value (SPT) </h4>
                                        <p></p>
                                        
                                            <div class="description"><p>We focus on areas that create value through our SPT initiative, which is a groupwide strategy focused on growing profitable market share in selected areas through integrated client-led asset and liability client value propositions.</p>
</div>
                                        
                                        
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        
                            <!-- col-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4 -->
                            <div class="columnsitem 4"> 
                                <div class="card nb-card">
                                    <div class="card-header leftalignedillustration bordered-header border-bottom-0">
                                        <div class="icon-wrapper ">
                                            <img src="/content/dam/group/icons/strategic-value-unlock-icon-06.svg" alt="Growth vectors" class="card-icon"/>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="card-body border-top-0">   
                                        <h4>Growth vectors</h4>
                                        <p></p>
                                        
                                            <div class="description"><p>Nedbank's growth vectors include portfolio diversification, including expansion into East Africa by leveraging our expertise and capabilities in CIB; the launch of a dedicated new offering to transform how mid-sized corporates access financial solutions through our Business and Commercial Banking cluster; unlocking faster growth and cross-sell and upsell of insurance products into our client base, with this supported by modernising payments and leveraging the investments we have made in IT.</p>
</div>
                                        
                                        
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        
                            <!-- col-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4 -->
                            <div class="columnsitem 5"> 
                                <div class="card nb-card">
                                    <div class="card-header leftalignedillustration bordered-header border-bottom-0">
                                        <div class="icon-wrapper ">
                                            <img src="/content/dam/group/icons/strategic-value-unlock-icon-03.svg" alt="Creating positive impacts" class="card-icon"/>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="card-body border-top-0">   
                                        <h4>Creating positive impacts</h4>
                                        <p></p>
                                        
                                            <div class="description"><p>For our business to succeed, we need a thriving economy, a well-functioning society, and a healthy environment. We also recognise that sustainability issues play a material role in shaping this system and setting the guardrails to optimise how we operate. </p>
</div>
                                        
                                        
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        
                    
                
                
                    
            </div>
        </div>
    </div></div>
