<h3>Corporate and Investment Banking (CIB)</h3>

<p><p>CIB is a market leader with strong expertise in commercial-property, renewable energy financing and corporate lending, as well as a strong South African trading franchise with excellent trading capabilities across all asset classes. It has leading expertise across various sectors such as mining, infrastructure financing, telecoms and public sectors.</p>
</p>

<div class="button-group">



        <a href="https://cib.nedbank.co.za/home.html" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" class="nbd-btn-tertiary" aria-label="Learn more Corporate and Investment Banking (CIB)" data-pagequicklinktype="link" data-pagequicklinkname="Learn more" data-pagequicklinklocation="Corporate and Investment Banking (CIB) | main content">Learn more
         <em class="tertiary-btn-icon right-arrow-btn"></em>
         </a>
 
