        <div class="nbd-bold-sub-title">
			<h4>CIB offers a full suite of wholesale banking solutions, including investment banking and corporate lending, global markets and treasury, commercial-property finance, transactional banking, deposit-taking products and services as well as our asset management business. Our client base includes corporates, financial institutions, state-owned entities and governments across Africa.</h4>
